	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="839"><a href="/en/archive/2016/14-refugees-fugitive-images-memory-in-motion/image-as-a-common-good.-on-laura-waddingtons-film-border">Image as a Common Good. On Laura Waddington's Film "Border"</a></h4>
